Title: The Status of String Theory

Comments: 16 pages, latex, two figures; minor corrections, references added

There have been many remarkable developments in our understanding ofsuperstring theory in the past few years, a period that has been described as``the second superstring revolution.'' Several of them are discussed here. Thepresentation is intended primarily for the benefit of nonexperts.